Also, keep sending your personal Spotify wrapped stats to my dms- I can’t express how good it feels to see myself in your top 5s!

NOVEMBER 16th, Alone* (*with a 4 piece band). I’m so excited to be at @chelseatableandstage. Come and join me, a killer band and two beautiful backing singers performing some of my music. Hear some old songs, some new songs, and listen to a story or two. Very excited to finally be back on the stage with my friends! Tickets at link in my bio.

November 3rd I’ll be releasing my next song “A Thousand Hours”. Co-written by @marricksmith - I’m really excited for this song to come out and be heard. I’ll be performing it live for the first time at my show on November 16th- buy your tickets at the link in bio. 

Can’t wait for y’all to hear this song!

Last week was such a dream. I performed my original music at @chelseatableandstage joined onstage by the most talented and wonderful humans/musicians, and then played the @austheatrefest cabaret at @thegreenroom42 with some more incredibly talented humans. Thank you to everyone who came- you made Thursday night a dream, and I felt so grateful to be surrounded by such love. 

Feeling very blessed and excited for the year ahead. 

Repping Australia and @cueclothingco at both, of course.
